There are three fundamental power series for all roots of a general
trinomial equations, each of them precisely corresponding
to the three analytic expressions described in the Appendix, two for
, and one for . Since our solutions lie within the
bound , only two of them will be of relevance.  We will
not discuss the general expansion for the general trinomial equation
() - interested readers are referred to
. However, the method discussed below is the same for any
trinomial equation.

